title: Ep134 Overkill Crimes
description: This week, the gals buckle down to cover some particularly gruesome crimes. Topics include the biological roots of rage, a very violent serial killer with a creepy thing for camping, and a man with a fatal foot fetish. Pop open a bottle of Winc's Pregame Red Blend, preemptively text your therapist, and get ready for Overkill Crimes.
